I"•0<h1 class="no_toc" id="molecular-dna-macro-files">Molecular DNA Macro Files</h1>

<p>Macro files define simulations in Geant4. Molecular DNA contains a number of additional 
commands that allow DNA simulations to take place. The full list of commands is written
in <a href="/molecular-docs/docs/overview/configuration">Configuration</a>.</p>

<h2 class="no_toc text-delta" id="table-of-contents">Table of contents</h2>

<ol id="markdown-toc">
